idget-woocommerce-product-short-description\" data-id=\"670942a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"woocommerce-product-short-description.default\">\r\n<div class=\"woocommerce-product-details__short-description\">\r\n<p><strong><span dir=\"auto\">How to Use 1/ Directions 1: Cook directly (Cooking)</span></strong><br><span dir=\"auto\">Step 1: Put the sauce packet, topping packet, vermicelli packet and satay packet (adequate amount) into the pot with 350-400ml of water, boil for about 3-5 minutes.</span></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">Step 2: Pour the cooked beef noodles into a bowl, add green onions and enjoy.</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span dir=\"auto\">Directions 2: Using a microwave</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">Step 1: Put all ingredients inside the package into a bowl with 350-400ml of boiling water or water at room temperature.</span></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">Step 2: Put the bowl in the microwave, select high power (180-200&deg;C) for 5-6 minutes with boiling water or 10-12 minutes with room temperature water.</span></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">Step 3: Remove bowl from microwave and enjoy.</span></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;Storage instructions:</span></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">Store frozen =&lt; 18&deg;C ​​or colder.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span dir=\"auto\">Expiry date: 2 years when the product is placed in the freezer at the correct temperature.</span></strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<footer class=\"elementor elementor-271 elementor-location-footer\" data-elementor-type=\"footer\" data-elementor-id=\"271\" data-elementor-post-type=\"elementor_library\">\r\n<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0187a43 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent e-lazyloaded\" data-id=\"0187a43\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\r\n<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\r\n<div class=\"elementor-element elemen