.9mg &ndash; 4%</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_kali\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\"><span dir=\"auto\">Potassium</span></th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">214.2mg &ndash; 4%</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_s%e1%ba%aft\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\"><span dir=\"auto\">Iron</span></th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">4.01mg &ndash; 23%</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong><span dir=\"auto\">Directions 1: Cooking</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">Step 1: Put the sauce packet, topping packet, noodle packet and satay packet (sufficient amount) into the pot with 400-450ml of water, boil for about 3-4 minutes.</span></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">Step 2: Pour the cooked fish cake noodle soup into a bowl, add green onions and enjoy.</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span dir=\"auto\">Directions 2: Using a microwave</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">Step 1: Put all ingredients inside the package into a bowl with 400-450ml of boiling water or water at room temperature.</span></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">Step 2: Put the bowl in the microwave, select high power (180-200&deg;C) for 5-6 minutes with boiling water or 10-12 minutes with room temperature water.</span></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">Step 3: Remove bowl from microwave and enjoy.</span></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">Storage instructions:</span></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">Store frozen =&lt; 18&deg;C ​​or colder.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span dir=\"auto\">Expiry date: 2 years when the product is placed in the freezer at the correct temperature.</span></strong></p>', '<p>C&agrave; M&egrave;n Foods\' fish cake banh canh is a perfect combination of traditional flavor and modern convenience. Each bowl of banh canh is a wonderful blend of soft, chewy banh canh noodles made from fresh rice flour and premium fish cakes &ndash; chewy, crispy, and flavorful, made from pure fresh fish, without impurities.</p>\r\n<p>The special feature that creates the uniqueness of C&agrave; M&egrave;n Foods\' fish cake banh canh is the rich broth, cooked from fish bones and natural vegetables, bringing a sweet, clear, yet rich taste. It comes with complete and fragrant spices, helping you easily prepare a full-flavored meal in just a few minutes.</p>\r\n<p>Without the use of preservatives, the product is preserved by modern freezing technology, maintaining its freshness and nutritional value. Enjoying C&agrave; M&egrave;n Foods\' fish cake banh canh means you are choosing a convenient, safe, and authentic home-style dish for yourself and your family &ndash; suitable for all meals from morning to night.</p>', 17, 2, '2025-12-03 10:47:27', '2025-12-03 11:12:04'),
