correct temperature.</span></strong></p>', '<p>Tuna noodle soup is a signature dish with a strong Central Vietnamese flavor, especially in Nha Trang, a place famous for its fresh seafood all year round. However, not everyone has the opportunity to enjoy this dish with the authentic local flavor, especially with today\'s busy life. That is why Ca Men Foods has researched and launched the frozen Nha Trang tuna noodle soup product line &ndash; full of nutrients, retaining the traditional flavor, and extremely convenient for modern users.</p>\r\n<p>The special feature of Ca Men tuna noodle soup lies not only in the naturally sweet broth simmered from fish bones, but also in the tuna pieces that are cleaned, quickly steamed to retain their tenderness, chewiness, and freshness, then frozen using international standard technology, helping to preserve their nutritional value. This is an ideal solution for those who want to eat delicious, safe, and time-saving meals without losing the authentic Vietnamese culinary experience.</p>', 18, 2, '2025-12-03 10:51:59', '2025-12-03 11:10:17'),
