and satay packet (adequate amount) into the pot with 350-400ml of water, boil for about 3-5 minutes.</span></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">Step 2: Pour the cooked snakehead fish noodle soup into a bowl, add green onions and enjoy.</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span dir=\"auto\">Directions 2: Using a microwave</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">Step 1: Put all ingredients inside the package into a bowl with 350-400ml of boiling water or water at room temperature.</span></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">Step 2: Put the bowl in the microwave, select high power (180-200&deg;C) for 8 minutes with boiling water or 12 minutes with room temperature water.</span></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">Step 3: Remove bowl from microwave and enjoy.</span></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;Storage instructions:</span></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">Store frozen =&lt; 18&deg;C ​​or colder.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span dir=\"auto\">Expiry date: 2 years when the product is placed in the freezer at the correct temperature.</span></strong></p>', '<p>Enjoy Ca Men Foods\' boneless snakehead fish cake soup, an appealing dish with a naturally sweet taste from fresh, delicious pieces of snakehead fish, carefully boned, firm, and rich in flavor. The soft, chewy sliced rice noodle strands and thick broth create a convenient, delicious, and nutritious meal for the whole family. In addition, Ca Men Foods\' snakehead fish cake soup contains shallots, which help reduce bloating and indigestion due to their antibacterial properties, eliminating harmful bacteria in the intestinal tract, making it suitable for beer drinkers or those with digestive problems.</p>\r\n<p>The unique highlight lies in the concentrated sauce packet, simmered from snakehead fish bones with natural spices, creating a rich, sweet flavor that recreates the standard taste of the cake soup. The product contains no preservatives, thanks to the application of deep freezing technology, preserving the freshness and original flavor of the snakehead fish. With just a few minutes of preparation, you have a hot bowl of boneless snakehead fish cake soup, convenient but still rich in culinary essence.</p>', 20, 2, '2025-12-03 11:01:22', '2025-12-03 11:11:26');
