uct-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_cholesterol\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\">Cholesterol</th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p>0mg &ndash; 0%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_sodiumnatri\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\">Sodium/Natri</th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p>1456mg &ndash; 63%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_t%e1%bb%95ng-carbohydrate\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\">Tổng carbohydrate</th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p>43.8g &ndash; 16%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_ch%e1%ba%a5t-x%c6%a1\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\">Chất xơ</th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p>3.52g &ndash; 13%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_t%e1%bb%95ng-%c4%91%c6%b0%e1%bb%9dng\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\">Tổng đường</th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p>0.91g</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_%c4%91%c6%b0%e1%bb%9dng-th%c3%aam-v%c3%a0o\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\">Đường th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o</th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p>0g &ndash; 0%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_ch%e1%ba%a5t-%c4%91%e1%ba%a1mprotein\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\">Chất đạm/Protein</th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p>8.31g &ndash; 17%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_vitamin-d\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\">Vitamin D</th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p>0mcg &ndash; 0%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_calciumcanxi\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\">Calcium/Canxi</th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p>151mg &ndash; 12%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_kali\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\">Kali</th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p>174mg &ndash; 4%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_s%e1%ba%aft\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\">Sắt</th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p>3.07mg &ndash; 17%</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>C&aacute;ch D&ugrave;ng 1/ Directions 1: Nấu trực tiếp (Cooking)</strong></p>\r\n<p>Bước 1: Cho g&oacute;i nước xốt, g&oacute;i topping, g&oacute;i miến v&agrave; g&oacute;i sa tế (liều lượng vừa đủ) v&agrave;o nồi với 450-500ml nước, đun s&ocirc;i khoảng 3-4 ph&uacute;t.</p>\r\n<p>Bước 2: Đổ miến lươn đ&atilde; ch&iacute;n ra t&ocirc;, cho th&ecirc;m h&agrave;nh l&aacute; v&agrave; thưởng thức</p>\r\n<p><strong>C&aacute;ch D&ugrave;ng 2/Directions 2: D&ugrave;ng l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng (Microwave)</strong></p>\r\n<p>Bước 1: Cho tất cả c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh phần b&ecirc;n trong bao b&igrave; v&agrave;o t&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng 450-500ml nước s&ocirc;i hoặc nước ở nhiệt độ thường.</p>\r\n<p>Bước 2: Cho t&ocirc; v&agrave;o l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng, chọn c&ocirc;ng suất cao (180-200&deg;C) thời gian 5-6 ph&uacute;t với nước s&ocirc;i hoặc 10-12 ph&uacute;t với nước nhiệt độ thường.</p>\r\n<p>Bước 3: Lấy t&ocirc; ra khỏi l&ograve; vi s&oacute;ng v&agrave; thưởng thức.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;Hướng dẫn bảo quản:</p>\r\n<p>Bảo qu&aacute;n đ&ocirc;ng lạnh =&lt; 18&deg;C hoặc lạnh hơn.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>HSD: 2 năm khi cho sản phẩm v&agrave;o ngăn đ&ocirc;ng tủ lạnh bảo quản đ&uacute;ng nhiệt độ</strong></p>', '<p class=\"QN2lPu\">Miến lươn C&agrave; M&egrave;n Foods mang đến trải nghiệm ẩm thực độc đ&aacute;o, đậm chất d&acirc;n d&atilde; nhưng vẫn tiện lợi v&agrave; tinh tế. Sợi miến dai mềm, kh&ocirc;ng bở n&aacute;t, thấm đẫm hương vị nước d&ugrave;ng đậm đ&agrave; được ninh từ xương ống v&agrave; lươn tươi, kết hợp c&ugrave;ng c&aacute;c loại gia vị truyền thống như h&agrave;nh phi, ti&ecirc;u xay, ớt bột&hellip; tạo n&ecirc;n hương thơm quyến rũ, kh&oacute; cưỡng.</p>\r\n<p class=\"QN2lPu\">Lươn trong sản phẩm được l&agrave;m sạch kỹ, lọc bỏ xương v&agrave; tẩm ướp chuẩn vị, sau đ&oacute; x&agrave;o săn hoặc chi&ecirc;n gi&ograve;n t&ugrave;y phi&ecirc;n bản, gi&uacute;p giữ trọn độ ngọt tự nhi&ecirc;n v&agrave; độ dai đặc trưng của thịt lươn. Mỗi g&oacute;i c&ograve;n k&egrave;m g&oacute;i nước d&ugrave;ng c&ocirc; đặc, gi&uacute;p t&aacute;i hiện trọn vẹn hương vị miến lươn chuẩn qu&aacute;n m&agrave; bạn c&oacute; thể thưởng thức ngay tại nh&agrave;.</p>\r\n<p class=\"QN2lPu\">Sản phẩm kh&ocirc;ng chất bảo quản, bảo quản bằng c&ocirc;ng nghệ cấp đ&ocirc;ng hiện đại, giữ nguy&ecirc;n chất lượng v&agrave; hương vị tươi ngon. Với miến lươn C&agrave; M&egrave;n Foods, chỉ trong v&agrave;i ph&uacute;t, bạn đ&atilde; c&oacute; ngay một t&ocirc; miến lươn n&oacute;ng hổi, thơm lừng &ndash; lựa chọn ho&agrave;n hảo cho những ai y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch ẩm thực truyền thống nhưng vẫn cần sự tiện lợi, nhanh gọn trong cuộc sống bận rộn.</p>', 21, 1, '2025-12-03 11:06:04', '2025-12-03 11:20:14'),
(42, 'Eel Vermicelli 3 packs', 'eel-vermicelli-3-packs', 'Ca Men Foods eel vermicelli – soft and chewy vermicelli, fresh and sweet boneless eel meat, soaked in broth simmered from marrow bones and eel, rich in authentic restaurant flavor.', '<table class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes shop_attributes\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; border-width: 2px;\" border=\"1\" aria-label=\"Product details\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_kh%e1%ba%a9u-ph%e1%ba%a7n-%c4%83n\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\"><span dir=\"auto\">Food rations</span></th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">100g</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_calories-n%c4%83ng-l%c6%b0%e1%bb%a3ng\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\"><span dir=\"auto\">Calories / Energy</span></th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">272</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_t%e1%bb%95ng-ch%e1%ba%a5t-b%c3%a9o\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\"><span dir=\"auto\">Total fat</span></th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">7.04g &ndash; 9%</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_ch%e1%ba%a5t-b%c3%a9o-b%c3%a3o-h%c3%b2a\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\"><span dir=\"auto\">Saturated fat</span></th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">0.85g &ndash; 4%</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_cholesterol\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\"><span dir=\"auto\">Cholesterol</span></th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">0mg &ndash; 0%</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_sodiumnatri\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\"><span dir=\"auto\">Sodium</span></th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">1456mg &ndash; 63%</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_t%e1%bb%95ng-carbohydrate\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\"><span dir=\"auto\">Total carbohydrates</span></th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">43.8g &ndash; 16%</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_ch%e1%ba%a5t-x%c6%a1\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\"><span dir=\"auto\">Fiber</span></th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">3.52g &ndash; 13%</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_t%e1%bb%95ng-%c4%91%c6%b0%e1%bb%9dng\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\"><span dir=\"auto\">Total sugar</span></th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">0.91g</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_%c4%91%c6%b0%e1%bb%9dng-th%c3%aam-v%c3%a0o\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\"><span dir=\"auto\">Added sugar</span></th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">0g &ndash; 0%</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_ch%e1%ba%a5t-%c4%91%e1%ba%a1mprotein\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\"><span dir=\"auto\">Protein</span></th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">8.31g &ndash; 17%</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_vitamin-d\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\"><span dir=\"auto\">Vitamin D</span></th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">0mcg &ndash; 0%</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_calciumcanxi\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\"><span dir=\"auto\">Calcium</span></th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">151mg &ndash; 12%</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_kali\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\"><span dir=\"auto\">Potassium</span></th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">174mg &ndash; 4%</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item woocommerce-product-attributes-item--attribute_s%e1%ba%aft\">\r\n<th class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__label\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\" scope=\"row\"><span dir=\"auto\">Iron</span></th>\r\n<td class=\"woocommerce-product-attributes-item__value\" style=\"border-width: 2px;\">\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">3.07mg &ndash; 17%</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong><span dir=\"auto\">Directions 1: Cooking</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">Step 1: Put the sauce packet, topping packet, vermicelli packet and satay packet (sufficient amount) into the pot with 450-500ml of water, boil for about 3-4 minutes.</span></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">Step 2: Pour the cooked eel vermicelli into a bowl, add green onions and enjoy.</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span dir=\"auto\">Directions 2: Using a microwave</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">Step 1: Put all ingredients inside the package into a bowl with 450-500ml of boiling water or water at room temperature.</span></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">Step 2: Put the bowl in the microwave, select high power (180-200&deg;C) for 5-6 minutes with boiling water or 10-12 minutes with room temperature water.</span></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">Step 3: Remove bowl from microwave and enjoy.</span></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;Storage instructions:</span></p>\r\n<p><span dir=\"auto\">Store frozen =&lt; 18&deg;C ​​or colder.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span dir=\"auto\">Expiry date: 2 years when the product is placed in the freezer at the correct temperature.</span></strong></p>', '<p>C&agrave; M&egrave;n Foods\' eel vermicelli offers a unique culinary experience, imbued with rustic charm yet convenient and refined. The vermicelli noodles are chewy and soft, not mushy, and soaked in the rich broth made from simmered bone broth and fresh eel, combined with traditional spices such as fried shallots, ground pepper, and chili powder, creating an irresistible, captivating aroma.</p>\r\n<p>The eel in the product is thoroughly cleaned, deboned, and marinated to perfection, then stir-fried or deep-fried depending on the version, helping to retain the natural sweetness and characteristic chewiness of the eel meat. Each package also includes a concentrated broth packet, allowing you to recreate the full flavor of authentic eel vermicelli that you can enjoy right at home.</p>\r\n<p>The product contains no preservatives and is preserved using modern freezing technology, maintaining the original quality and fresh taste. With C&agrave; M&egrave;n Foods\' eel vermicelli, in just a few minutes, you\'ll have a hot, fragrant bowl of eel vermicelli &ndash; the perfect choice for those who love traditional cuisine but still need convenience and speed in a busy life.</p>', 21, 2, '2025-12-03 11:06:04', '2025-12-03 11:20:14'),
